---
layout: page
title: "Meus trabalhos"
permalink: "/portfolio/index.html"
description: "Uma seleção de projetos variando de desenvolvimento front-end ao design de interface, focada em
performance e usabilidade."
---

{% set projects = portfolio.projects %}
{% set categories = portfolio.categories %}
{% set stats = portfolio.stats %}

<section class="pb-32 space-y-32">
  {% for project in projects %}
  <article class="portfolio-item flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-24 group">
    <figure
      class="w-full lg:w-1/2 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-border-dark bg-white dark:bg-card-dark transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10">
      <img alt="{{ project.imageAlt or project.title }}"
        class="w-full aspect-video object-cover transition-transform duration-500" src="{{ project.image }}">
    </figure>
    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 space-y-6">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <span class="text-brand-blue-500 font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">
          {{ project.category | join(' & ') or "Redesign & Acessibilidade" }}
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold hover:text-primary transition-colors">
          <a href="{{ project.url or project.links.demo }}"
            class="text-white hover:text-brand-blue-500 transition-colors">{{
            project.title }}</a>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
        {{ project.description }}
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        {% for tech in project.technologies %}
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-border-dark rounded-full text-sm">{{ tech }}</span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
  {% endfor %}
</section>

<section class="container mx-auto px-6 mb-32">
  <div class="bg-brand-dark-900 border border-brand-gray-200/30 rounded-3xl p-12 md:p-20 text-center space-y-8">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-blue-500">Vamos construir algo juntos?</h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-brand-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Estou sempre aberto a novos projetos, mentorias e colaborações interessantes em engenharia de software e design.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6 pt-4">
      <a class="bg-brand-blue-500 hover:bg-brand-blue-600 text-brand-dark-500 no-underline px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1 w-full sm:w-auto"
        href="/contato">
        Entre em contato
      </a>
      <a class="text-brand-blue-500 hover:underline font-semibold text-lg flex items-center gap-2 group" href="/cv">
        Veja meu currículo
        {% lucide "arrow-right", { class: "group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" } %}
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>